Small Tutorial for TwinSaga.TO Players.

1. Download on Steam the Official Twin Saga Game
2. Replace all the Files with TwinSaga.TO Client Files on ur SteamLibrary Path
\SteamLibrary\steamapps\common\TwinSaga

3. Start ur Game on Steam, it started the TS.TO Launcher and the Steam Overlay into ur Game.

3.1 For People they needed Playtime on Steam, Start again on Steam TwinSaga and dont click Start, the Launcher must open to get more Playtimes.
